{
  "stem": "14060.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 1.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "By the time somebody did something serious, then you really had to run away to America.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So practically, what I am trying to say is that after the war, I had absolutely no relations on anywhere near or far away.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Apparently, I'm told, that there is a film producer called Weiler-- his name I've seen many times on films-- that he seemingly is a relation of ours.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But to be honest with you, as he wasn't looking for me, I wasn't looking for him, maybe not nice of me, but as I don't want to have any favors, as I'm perfectly OK without it.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I'm told that he was apparently some distant family of ours, whose maybe parents or grandparents emigrated to America.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he spells his name with a Y, not W-E-I-L-E-R.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, the events of the pre-war period had various personal anecdotes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And if I just may for a second refer to my notes, because once I remember things, I want to give you all the details in a more chronological order that it makes sense to a person who hears the story for the first time.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It certainly makes sense to me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now coming to the difficulties created by this rampant, ongoing anti-Semitism, I want to tell in our town the specific division and mentality of the population.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The Hungarians hated the Jews, because they considered them aliens.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The German minority hated them for the same reason.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were quite well to do, the German minorities.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Mainly agriculture holdings, they had, quite well-to-do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they were called bohnenzuchter-- ponzichter, which means bohnenzuchter, which the exact translation is bean-growers, Because it was a bean-growing area.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was a very good agriculturally rich area.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they obviously were influenced by events taking on in Germany.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
